| Package         | Use Case                                     |
| --------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| `flask`         | Serves the AI model through a web API        |
| `flask-cors`    | Allows frontend (JavaScript) to call backend |
| `tensorflow`    | Deep learning library to train and run model |
| `numpy`         | Image/matrix manipulation                    |
| `opencv-python` | Image preprocessing (grayscale, resize)      |
| `pillow`        | Basic image operations like loading/saving   |
| `scikit-learn`  | For model evaluation and preprocessing tools |
| `matplotlib`    | For visualizing digit data if needed         |
| Component          | Minimum Recommendation         |
| ------------------ | ------------------------------ |
| Python version     | 3.7 â€“ 3.10                     |
| RAM                | 4GB+                           |
| GPU (for training) | NVIDIA CUDA-enabled (optional) |
